snippet.title: Shawn Wasabi - BURNT RICE [Original Song]
snippet.description:

YUNG GEMMY 
Soundcloud: https://soundcloud.com/yung-gemmy 
Twitter: https://twitter.com/YUNG_GEMMY 
Instagram: https://instagram.com/yunggemmy

Shawn Wasabi is a visionary artist and producer renowned for his hits “Marble Soda,” “Burnt Rice,” “Hotto Dogu,” “Otter Pop,” “Spicy Boyfriend,” and “I Lost All My Eggs.” He worked with artists like Hollis, Raychel Jay, and Yung Gemmy — amassing millions of streams and co-invented the 64-button “Midi Fighter 64” controller.
